{
  "description": "隐藏称号系统 — 可叠加获取，按结算组别分类。",
  "groups": [
    {
      "group": "课程点名组",
      "titles": [
        {
          "id": "class_stable_student",
          "name": "课堂稳定器",
          "subtitle": "稳定上课",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "classAttendCount", "op": ">=", "value": 8 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "skipClassCount", "op": "<=", "value": 1 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "teacherTrust", "op": ">=", "value": 20 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你大多数时候都坐在教室里。它不传奇，但足够稳定，也足够让老师记住你是个靠谱的人。"
        },
        {
          "id": "class_honest_repair",
          "name": "迟到补锅人",
          "subtitle": "诚实补救",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "returnClassCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
            { "kind": "meta", "desc": "经常在被点名时选择'立刻赶回教室'或主动解释" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你犯过错，但也愿意补救。这个学期没有完美答案，只有一次次赶回去的选择。"
        },
        {
          "id": "class_roll_call_survivor",
          "name": "点名边缘人",
          "subtitle": "点名幸存",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "skipClassCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "rollCallSavedCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你不是没逃过课，只是每次危险都差一点擦肩而过。点名册上有你的传说，也有你的冷汗。"
        },
        {
          "id": "class_absence_warning",
          "name": "缺勤边缘户",
          "subtitle": "缺勤预警",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "skipClassCount", "op": ">=", "value": 5 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "absencePenaltyCount", "op": ">=", "value": 3 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "teacherTrust", "op": "<=", "value": 10 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你获得了很多自由时间，也把自己推到了危险边缘。老师的点名册成了你本学期最大的敌人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "group": "社交互助组",
      "titles": [
        {
          "id": "friend_reliable_partner",
          "name": "靠谱同桌",
          "subtitle": "可靠搭档",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendBond", "op": ">=", "value": 6 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendHelpCount", "op": ">=", "value": 3 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "这个学期里，你们不只是普通同学。你帮过他，他也在关键时候拉过你一把。"
        },
        {
          "id": "friend_roll_call_buddy",
          "name": "点名互保人",
          "subtitle": "点名战友",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendRollCallHelpCount", "op": ">=", "value": 1 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你们的关系有点微妙，但有一件事很确定：点名发生时，他真的帮你挡过一次风。"
        },
        {
          "id": "friend_exam_ally",
          "name": "资料共享者",
          "subtitle": "考前伙伴",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "sharedNotes", "op": "eq", "value": true },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendReviewCount", "op": ">=", "value": 1 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你们靠互相分享资料撑过了考试。成绩也许不是奇迹，但至少不是孤军奋战。"
        },
        {
          "id": "friend_nodding_terms",
          "name": "点头之交",
          "subtitle": "普通同学",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendBond", "op": ">=", "value": 0 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendBond", "op": "<=", "value": 2 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendHelpCount", "op": "<=", "value": 1 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你们认识，但没有真正走近。校园里很多关系都是这样，停在见面点头的距离。"
        },
        {
          "id": "friend_read_ignored",
          "name": "已读不回的人",
          "subtitle": "关系冷淡",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendRefuseCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "friendBond", "op": "<", "value": 0 }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "对方后来很少再找你。你们没有吵架，只是自然地疏远了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "group": "社团活动组",
      "titles": [
        {
          "id": "club_backbone",
          "name": "社团主心骨",
          "subtitle": "核心成员",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubType", "op": "neq", "value": "none" },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubContribution", "op": ">=", "value": 6 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubShowcaseSuccess", "op": "eq", "value": true }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "社团里每个人都知道——真有事的时候，找你就对了。"
        },
        {
          "id": "club_mediator",
          "name": "气氛修补匠",
          "subtitle": "折中协调",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubRelation", "op": ">=", "value": 5 },
            { "kind": "meta", "desc": "社团分歧时选择了'协调折中方案'" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你在团队最混乱的时候站了出来，用耐心和沟通把大家重新捏合在一起。"
        },
        {
          "id": "club_showcase_star",
          "name": "展示担当",
          "subtitle": "台上亮眼",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubShowcaseScore", "op": ">=", "value": 18 },
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "expressionUnlocked", "op": "eq", "value": true },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "social", "op": ">=", "value": 50 }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你站在台上的那一刻，所有人都看了过来。你的表现没有辜负社团一学期的努力。"
        },
        {
          "id": "club_steady_member",
          "name": "稳定成员",
          "subtitle": "踏实参与",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubActivityCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubContribution", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubContribution", "op": "<=", "value": 5 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你不是社团里最耀眼的，但你每一次任务都没有掉链子。稳定本身就是一种贡献。"
        },
        {
          "id": "club_ghost_member",
          "name": "社团幽灵成员",
          "subtitle": "若有若无",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubType", "op": "neq", "value": "none" },
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubActivityCount", "op": "<=", "value": 1 },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubContribution", "op": "<", "value": 0 }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你在社团名单上，但大家对你的印象很模糊。有时候连你自己都忘了自己加入了什么社团。"
        },
        {
          "id": "club_free_spirit",
          "name": "自由时间守护者",
          "subtitle": "不加入社团",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "clubType", "op": "eq", "value": "none" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你没有加入任何社团。你把时间留给了自己，这也是一种生活态度。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "group": "大创专属组",
      "titles": [
        {
          "id": "innovation_campus_star",
          "name": "校园创新之星",
          "subtitle": "优秀项目",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "excellent" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你的项目不仅是完成，更是出彩。校园里开始有人打听你的名字和作品。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_team_harmony",
          "name": "和谐团队",
          "subtitle": "团队信任",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationTeamTrust", "op": ">=", "value": 40 },
            { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "neq", "value": "failed" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "不管最终结果如何，你的队伍始终没有散。这种信任比任何分数都难得。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_firefighter",
          "name": "通宵救火队长",
          "subtitle": "最佳救火",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "firefighter" },
                {
                  "kind": "group",
                  "require": "all",
                  "conditions": [
                    { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationCrisisCount", "op": ">=", "value": 2 },
                    { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationProgress", "op": ">=", "value": 60 }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "每一次危机你都顶了上去。虽然过程惊心动魄，但你的熬夜和汗水没有白费。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_completed",
          "name": "稳定结项人",
          "subtitle": "顺利结项",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "completed" }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你的项目顺利通过了。没有惊艳全场，但也绝对没有翻车。这份稳定值得肯定。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_ppt_master",
          "name": "PPT 保命大师",
          "subtitle": "勉强通过",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "pass" },
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationDemoMode", "op": "eq", "value": "safe" },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationDefenseScore", "op": ">=", "value": 25 }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你的实际成果可能不多，但你的 PPT 帮你活了下来。有些时候，包装也是一种能力。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_silent",
          "name": "项目群沉默者",
          "subtitle": "项目翻车",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "failed" },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationTeamTrust", "op": "<=", "value": 0 }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "大创群的消息提示从此不再响起。有些事，不提也罢。"
        },
        {
          "id": "innovation_bystander",
          "name": "大创旁观者",
          "subtitle": "没有参加",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "kind": "group",
              "require": "any",
              "conditions": [
                { "kind": "enum", "stat": "innovationResult", "op": "eq", "value": "bystander" },
                { "kind": "stat", "stat": "innovationJoined", "op": "eq", "value": false }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "大创的展板和答辩教室，你只是路过。这不是你的赛道，没关系。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "group": "日常积累组",
      "titles": [
        {
          "id": "daily_morning_runner",
          "name": "早八冲刺王",
          "subtitle": "冲刺救场",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "lateCount", "op": ">=", "value": 5 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你用脚步声证明了自己还想上课。老师可能不完全满意，但至少看见了你冲进教室的残影。"
        },
        {
          "id": "daily_library_dweller",
          "name": "图书馆钉子户",
          "subtitle": "常驻图书馆",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "libraryVisitCount", "op": ">=", "value": 10 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "图书馆的某个角落几乎成了你的专属工位。管理员开始对你点头了。"
        },
        {
          "id": "daily_cafeteria_resident",
          "name": "食堂常驻居民",
          "subtitle": "按时吃饭",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "mealCount", "op": ">=", "value": 20 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "你把食堂当成了家的延伸。每一顿饭都没有落下。"
        },
        {
          "id": "daily_night_shift_champion",
          "name": "夜班战神",
          "subtitle": "深夜兼职",
          "conditions": [
            { "kind": "stat", "stat": "storeNightShiftCount", "op": ">=", "value": 5 }
          ],
          "require": "all",
          "text": "当校园沉入黑暗，你的工作才刚刚开始。便利店夜班是你最熟悉的战场。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}